eturns: 1</pre></td></tr><tr><td class="statText"><table><tr><td colspan="2" class="statText"><p>This input represents a BST of the following shape:     </p>
<p><img src="http://www.topcoder.com/contest/problem/ConstructBST/bst_ex1.jpg"></p>
<p>Using the characters {'A','B'}, only the string <tt>"BA"</tt> can generate a tree with the given shape.</p></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td align="center" nowrap class="statText">1)</td><td class="statText"></td></tr><tr><td class="statText">    </td><td class="statText"><table><tr><td class="statText"><table><tr><td class="statText"><pre>{1, 3, 6}</pre></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td class="statText"><pre>Returns: 1</pre></td></tr><tr><td class="statText"><table><tr><td colspan="2" class="statText"><p>This input represents a BST of the following shape:     </p>
